<p>To translate that quote in English, he declared some important points:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Impurity Function (A function for evaluating the performance of classification)</li>
  <li>The more classes in one node to be classified, the higher impurity, and vice versa.</li>
  <li>Purpose is to obtain the impurity as small as possible covered all nodes.</li>
</ul>

